  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD COMMUNITY</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>OneKind </strong> His game is a hide-and-seek game involving a hunter, multiple cows and rabbits.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hunter Role </strong></h2>He has to kill the bad animals on his farm with his axe and protect his own psychology.<br>Meanwhile, he must also consider his axe-throwing rights and make sure to hit the demonic animals.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978220/extras/6840ab44dc66310c9e0f8262f273b37d.poster.avif?t=1732304168\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978220/extras/6840ab44dc66310c9e0f8262f273b37d.webm?t=1732304168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978220/extras/6840ab44dc66310c9e0f8262f273b37d.mp4?t=1732304168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Cow Role  </strong></h2>To blend in with the AIs on the map to avoid the hunter, manage hunger and thirst bars to survive, and be the last one standing by betraying the rabbit and making it bait for the hunter.<br>It's time to show your kicks to the hunter.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978220/extras/4c70539b455717df3ea4a7f5f4f40698.poster.avif?t=1732304168\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978220/extras/4c70539b455717df3ea4a7f5f4f40698.webm?t=1732304168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978220/extras/4c70539b455717df3ea4a7f5f4f40698.mp4?t=1732304168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rabbit Role </strong></h2>Your aim is to mix with the AIs on the map, avoid the hunter, slow down the hunter, survive by controlling the hunger and thirst bars, and reveal the cow to the hunter in order to be the last one standing.Your footprints are so cute, but don't leave yourself thirsty!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978220/extras/94c6a146386eed8f2718512bb056a5c3.poster.avif?t=1732304168\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978220/extras/94c6a146386eed8f2718512bb056a5c3.webm?t=1732304168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978220/extras/94c6a146386eed8f2718512bb056a5c3.mp4?t=1732304168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
